nclude by extending our results to the\ncorresponding forward process, understood in the sense of Letac (1986), namely,\nthe reflected process $M_n^\\ast := \\max\\{ A_n M_{n-1}^\\ast + B_n, 0 \\}$ for $n\n\\in {\\mathbb N}$, where $M_0^\\ast=0$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 27 Nov 2014 20:18:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-12-01"}
