s to the accumulation of a decade of INTEGRAL\ndata, with observations covering the whole orbit several times, allowing us to\ndetect an asymmetric pattern in the orbital distribution of off-states in Vela\nX-1.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 28 Nov 2014 13:55:33 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 7 Jan 2015 11:17:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-01-08"}
